<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <body style='font-family: -apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Roboto,Oxygen-Sans,Ubuntu,Cantarell,"Helvetica Neue",sans-serif;'>
        <div style="background-color: cornflowerblue; height: 64px; line-height: 64px; color: #fff; border-radius: 3px;">
            <h1 style="padding: 10px; line-height: 1.8; text-align: center;">Supporttool</h1>
        </div>
        <div style="border-radius: 5px; background-color: #fff; border: 1px solid darkgrey; margin: 5px; padding: 0 10px; box-shadow: 1px 1px #0000008c; color: #000">
            <p>Sehr geehrte Damen und Herren,</p>
            <p>es wurde soeben ein neues Ticket erstellt. Der Kunde erwartet innerhalb der nächsten 24 Stunden eine Erstantwort.</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Name des Kunden: {{ name }}</li>
                <li>Ticketnummer: {{ id }}</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="{{ url }}/Ticket/{{ id }}" style="background-color:cornflowerblue;border-bottom-color:rgb(255,255,255);border-bottom-left-radius:2px;border-bottom-right-radius:2px;border-bottom-style:none;border-bottom-width:0;border-image-outset:0;border-image-repeat:stretch;border-image-slice:100%;border-image-source:none;border-image-width:1;border-left-color:rgb(255,255,255);border-left-style:none;border-left-width:0;border-right-color:rgb(255,255,255);border-right-style:none;border-right-width:0;border-top-color:rgb(255,255,255);border-top-left-radius:2px;border-top-right-radius:2px;border-top-style:none;border-top-width:0;box-shadow:rgba(0,0,0,.14) 0 2px 2px 0,rgba(0,0,0,.12) 0 3px 1px -2px,rgba(0,0,0,.2) 0 1px 5px 0;box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(255,255,255);cursor:pointer;display:inline-block;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Oxygen-Sans,Ubuntu,Cantarell,'Helvetica Neue',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:400;height:36px;letter-spacing:.5px;line-height:36px;outline-color:rgb(255,255,255);outline-style:none;outline-width:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:16px;padding-right:16px;padding-top:0;text-align:center;text-decoration-color:rgb(255,255,255);text-decoration-line:none;text-decoration-style:solid;text-size-adjust:100%;text-transform:uppercase;transition-delay:0s;transition-duration:0.2s;transition-property:background-color;transition-timing-function:ease-out;vertical-align:middle;width:173.438px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);">Direkt zum Ticket {{ id }}</a>
            <p>Mit freundlichen Grüßen,</p>
            <p>Ihr Support Team</p>
        </div>
        <div style="background: #808585 !important; color: #fff !important; height: 130px; padding-left: 20px; border-radius: 3px">
            <div style="width: 50%; float: left; background: inherit;"><h2>Generelle Information</h2><p>Logge dich ein um zu deiner Ticketansicht zu gelangen. Ein Suppoortmitarbeiter wird versuchen dir schnellstmöglich weiterzuhelfen.</p></div>
            <div style="width: 25%; float: left; background: inherit;"><h2>Links</h2><a style="color: #fff" href="{{ url }}">Zur Website</a></div>
            <div style="width: 25%; float: left; background: inherit;"></div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
